import React from 'react' import { useSelector, useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { getTasks } from '../features/task/taskSlice' const UserDashboard = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const { task } = useSelector(state => state.task) useEffect(() => { dispatch(getTasks()) }, []) return (
{task?.map((tas) => {
Song Artist Year
The Sliding Mr. Bones (Next Stop, Pottersville) Malcolm Lockyer 1961
Witchy Woman The Eagles 1972
Shining Star Earth, Wind, and Fire 1975
})}
) } export default UserDashboard
